short_description: CVC check fails

short_description: Postal code check fails

short_description: Line1 check fails
description: The address line 1 check fails.\nThe payment succeeds unless you block it with a custom Radar rule.

short_description: Address checks fail

short_description: Address unavailable

Fraudulent
description: With default account settings, charge succeeds, only to be disputed as fraudulent. This type of dispute is protected after 3D Secure authentication.

short_description: Not received
description: With default account settings, charge succeeds, only to be disputed as product not received. This type of dispute isn’t protected after 3D Secure authentication.

short_description: Enquiry
description: With default account settings, charge succeeds, only to be disputed as an inquiry.

short_description: Warning
description: With default account settings, charge succeeds, only to receive an early fraud warning.

short_description: The dispute is closed and marked as won. Your account is credited the amount of the charge and related fees.
The dispute is closed and marked as lost. Your account isn’t credited.
Asynchronous success
description: The charge succeeds. If you initiate a refund, its status begins as pending. Some time later, its status transitions to succeeded and sends a charge.refund.updated webhook event.

short_description: Asynchronous failure
description: The charge succeeds. If you initiate a refund, its status begins as succeeded. Some time later, its status transitions to failed and sends a charge.refund.updated webhook event.

short_description: Bypass pending balance
description: The US charge succeeds. Funds are added directly to your available balance, bypassing your pending balance.

short_description: Bypass pending balance
description: The international charge succeeds. Funds are added directly to your available balance, bypassing your pending balance.

short_description: Authenticate unless set up
description: This card requires authentication for every payment unless you set it up for future payments. After you set it up, it no longer requires authentication.

short_description: Always authenticate
description: This card requires authentication on all transactions, regardless of how the card is set up.

short_description: Already set up
description: This card is already set up for off-session use. It requires authentication for one-off and other on-session payments. However, all off-session payments succeed as if the card has been previously set up.

short_description: Insufficient funds
description: This card requires authentication for one-off payments. All payments are be declined with an insufficient_funds failure code even after being succes

short_description: 3DS2 Required - OK
description: 3D Secure 2 authentication must be completed for the payment to be successful.By default, your Radar rules request 3D Secure authentication for this card.

short_description: 3DS Required - OK
description: 3D Secure authentication must be completed for the payment to be successful. By default, your Radar rules request 3D Secure authentication for this card.

short_description: 3DS Required - Declined
description: 3D Secure authentication is required, but payments are declined with a card_declined failure code after authentication. By default, your Radar rules request 3D Secure authentication for this card.

short_description: 3DS Required - Outcome: Error
description: 3D Secure authentication is required, but the 3D Secure lookup request fails with a processing error. Payments are declined with a card_declined failure code. By default, your Radar rules request 3D Secure authentication for this card.

short_description: 3DS Supported - Outcome: OK
description: 3D Secure authentication might still be performed, but isn’t required. By default, your Radar rules don’t request 3D Secure authentication for this card.

short_description: 3DS Supported - Outcome: Error
description: 3D Secure authentication might still be performed, but isn’t required. However, attempts to perform 3D Secure result in a processing error. By default, your Radar rules don’t request 3D Secure authentication for this card.

short_description: 3DS Supported - Outcome: Unenrolled
description: 3D Secure is supported for this card, but this card isn’t enrolled in 3D Secure. This means that if your Radar rules request 3D Secure, the customer doesn’t go through additional authentication. By default, your Radar rules don’t request 3D Secure authentication for this card.

short_description: 3DS Not supported
description: 3D Secure isn’t supported on this card and can’t be invoked. The PaymentIntent proceeds without performing authentication.

short_description: Out of band
description: 3D Secure 2 authentication must be completed on all transactions. Triggers the challenge flow with Out of Band UI.

short_description: One time passcode
description: 3D Secure 2 authentication must be completed on all transactions. Triggers the challenge flow with One Time Passcode UI.

short_description: Single select
description: 3D Secure 2 authentication must be completed on all transactions. Triggers the challenge flow with single-select UI.

short_description: Multi select
description: 3D Secure 2 authentication must be completed on all transactions. Triggers the challenge flow with multi-select UI.

short_description: Webview
description: 3D Secure authentication must be completed for the payment to be successful. Triggers the challenge flow using a webview. You can check that your return_url dismisses the modal.

short_description: Offline PIN
description: This card simulates a payment where the cardholder is prompted for and enters an offline PIN. The resulting charge has cardholder_verification_method set to offline_pin.

short_description: Offline PIN retry
description: Simulates an SCA-triggered retry flow where a cardholder’s initial contactless charge fails and the reader then prompts the user to insert their card and enter their offline PIN. The resulting charge has cardholder_verification_method set to offline_pin.

short_description: Online PIN

short_description: Online PIN retry
